title: PAX AUS 2019
body: Hey! Just wondering if Riot is planning to be at PAX AUS this year? If someone from the team could get back to me that would be great! {{sticker:sg-lux-2}}

replies.body: As far as I know, there will be a Riot presence at PAX AUS this year, though I don't think you'll find any solid info about it yet (perhaps it's one of the "secrets" in the schedule).
Awesome! Thanks for getting back to me!
